* Iron Raptor tryed to get up but her broken leg could never manage her 
weight now, she wriggles on her side trying to get away from Inferno's 
flame.
There is no way that she could move out of the flame's path so she did the 
next thing that came in her mind...she swung her head around and slammed it 
into Inferno with all of her power.
She was bleeding, had a broken leg, and now she was slightly burned, she was 
hurt and angry! Soon she would only be running on adrenalin!*
